The phrase "very serious production-grade system" in this context refers to the complexity and robustness of ChatGPT. It indicates that ChatGpt is not a simple or basic system, but a fully developed, complex one that has been built to a high standard of quality and efficiency. It is designed for "production" use in real-world applications and scenarios, rather than just being a prototype or an experiment. It is also considered "serious" as it has undergone serious research, rigorous testing, and continuous refinement by professionals. Therefore, it won't be easy to reproduce it due to its level of sophistication and complexity.